uot;23&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> HorizontalAlignment</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Left&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Margin</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;187,32,0,0&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Name</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;textBox1&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> VerticalAlignment</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Top&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Width</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;120&quot; /&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Button</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Height</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;23&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> HorizontalAlignment</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Left&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Margin</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;349,32,0,0&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Name</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;button1&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> VerticalAlignment</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Top&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Width</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;75&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Click</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;button1_Click&quot;&gt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Go</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Button</span><span style=\"