    "Html": "<p>Hi, <br>\r\n<br>\r\nI have figured it out, actually it is very simple and i have just done it by using datatable and OleDbReader.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHere is sample code:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px\"></span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">private</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">void</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> button1_Click(</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">object</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> sender, </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">RoutedEventArgs</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> e)\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>{</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">OleDbConnection</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> myConn = </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">new</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">OleDbConnection</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">(\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">@&quot;Provider=Microsoft.Jet.OLEDB.4.0; Data Source=C:\\\\App_Data\\\\Database2.mdb&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">);\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">OleDbCommand</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> myCommand;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>myCommand = </p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">new</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">OleDbCommand</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">&quot;Select * From registrant where registrantid =&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> + textBox1.Text.ToString() , myConn);\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">DataTable</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> dt = </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">new</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">DataTable</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">();\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">try\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px\">\r\n<p>{</p>\r\n<p>myConn.Open();</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">OleDbDataReader</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> reader;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>reader = myCommand.ExecuteReader();</p>\r\n<p>dt.Load(reader);</p>\r\n<p>dataGrid1.ItemsSource = dt.DefaultView;</p>\r\n<p>myConn.Close();</p>\r\n<p>}</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">catch</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> (</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">OleDbException</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> a)\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>{</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">Console</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">.WriteLine(</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">&quot;Error: {0}&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">, a.Errors[0].Message);\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>}</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>}</p>\r\n<p><br>\r\nThanks..</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n",
